121
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,040
sokongan keluarga Zhuang

122
00:06:20,040 --> 00:06:21,680
dan sentiasa berjaga-jaga terhadap mereka.

123
00:06:21,680 --> 00:06:22,920
Bagaimana anda boleh mengajar saya untuk…

124
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:23,580
Chengyang!

125
00:06:24,040 --> 00:06:25,630
Anda kini Maharaja.

126
00:06:25,950 --> 00:06:26,680
Anda tidak boleh

127
00:06:27,310 --> 00:06:28,750
pernah cakap macam tu lagi.

128
00:06:30,120 --> 00:06:30,750
okay,

129
